<span id="freeTextContainer11754655858626116727">What a fucking stunning book. <br/><br/>I don&apos;t normally curse in reviews, but I can&apos;t properly express my deep and unwavering adoration for <i>The Short Life of Sparrows</i> any other way. It was beautifully written. I feel like I&apos;ve known the characters for years. The plot was interesting and unexpected. I basically fell in love after the first sentence, and I think fantasy fans and romance fans alike will feel the same way. I can&apos;t wait to read more from the author, and if there&apos;s ever a sequel, I&apos;ll be the f</span>
