          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1456854524" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17792557952486771434">The Short Life of Sparrows is a awesome read, I loved it, Loved it.<br/>I fell in love with the characters and the world that Emm Cole created fairly early on, I was hooked. I found myself looking forward to any free time I had so I would get a chance to read a few chapters.<br/>The Short Life of Sparrows has it all action, friendship, love, loss, pain, magic, it really does have everything.<br/>This book came highly recommended to me from my bestie, she told me that it was/is right up my alley, as there are w</span>
  <span id="freeText17792557952486771434" style="display:none">The Short Life of Sparrows is a awesome read, I loved it, Loved it.<br />I fell in love with the characters and the world that Emm Cole created fairly early on, I was hooked. I found myself looking forward to any free time I had so I would get a chance to read a few chapters.<br />The Short Life of Sparrows has it all action, friendship, love, loss, pain, magic, it really does have everything.<br />This book came highly recommended to me from my bestie, she told me that it was/is right up my alley, as there are witches and warlocks. <br />My only complaint is that it sat on my bookshelf for so long before I got to it. <br /><br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="17792557952486771434" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
